<div id="history">
    <h3>History</h3>
    <p class=displaytext>The year 1999 marked the launch of ICFS, one of  the largest, most proactive student societies in the country. From around 250  members at that time, we have grown to over 2400 members at present through  pro-actively developing our offering to our members and sponsors. During this  time we have forged strong links to some of the largest and most prestigious  firms in industry. Throughout this time we have received the full backing of  the Imperial College Business School, and we continue to work closely with them.</p>               
